Package: direct
Type: Package
Title: MCP Tools for Claude Desktop + RStudio Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Mischke", email = "modokrit@gmail.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides Model Context Protocol (MCP) tools that enable Claude Desktop 
    to interact with RStudio projects. Includes safe file operations, code execution, 
    and workspace management with built-in security features. Extends the 'btw' package
    with active execution capabilities while btw provides passive observation.
